title: Ranked TT?? Does it exist??

embed.description: League of Legends (LoL) Summoner Search, Stats, Replay, Spectating, Current Game, Ranking, Match History

body:
Can riot advertise in the client or something when it's live. If they did a survey of people to figure out who actually knows the schedule for it I'm pretty sure 90% percent of people wouldn't have a clue when ranked TT flex queue is Live. How can the queue be healthy if most people don't even know of its existence?? 

There is legit 14 people silver 1 in the top 200 in OCE (according to LOLSTARZ)

Im pretty sure its live on Thursday afternoons but i don't even know.

replies.body:
There is a stickied thread with the details...

"Twisted Treeline Ranked Flex:
Thursday: 3:00pm - 1:00am AEDT"

http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/wgM0WBsO-queue-schedule-updated-dec-1st
